Class YamlConfiguration

java.lang.Object
com.github.siroshun09.configapi.api.AbstractConfiguration
com.github.siroshun09.configapi.api.file.AbstractFileConfiguration
com.github.siroshun09.configapi.yaml.YamlConfiguration
All Implemented Interfaces:
Configuration, FileConfiguration, AutoCloseable
public class YamlConfiguration extends AbstractFileConfiguration
A class that implements Configuration for Yaml file.

This class can load from or save to Yaml file.

In the internal, this manages keys and values in MappedConfiguration.
